3. cs.SI (Signal Processing) - The paper involves the processing of signals in MIMO channels, which is a fundamental aspect of signal processing. 
4. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses the optimization of power allocation in MIMO channels, which is relevant to networking and internet architecture.
